{"tid":1029072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警認賣丁權獲20萬報酬","createTime":"2019-02-20T03:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T06:32:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c43761cb844ac34936fa260523fe7f9056b46084","tid":1029072,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190220/20616665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616665&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n88F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9b2f2db1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616665&h=2ef1faa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190220/20616665</a><br />\n<br />\n男警認賣丁權獲20萬報酬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190220/large/20la3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F20la3p3.jpg&h=9b2244a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【騙助學金案 】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】26歲男警員涉於求學期間隱瞞擁有套丁得來的12幅大埔土地，成功獲逾19.3萬元助學金，事後聲稱估計該批漏報土地是親戚所贈。警員昨出庭自辯，對於呈堂兩份由發展商轉讓涉案12幅共值125萬的土地的轉讓契上面有其簽名，聲稱毫無印象，只知讓出丁權就能獲得20萬報酬，至於是否認識賣家及其授權人，文件是否由他簽署，他大多答不知道、不清楚、沒印象。<br />\n<br />\n被告古俊輝（圖）被控兩項欺詐罪，他供稱村內司理在2010年得悉他快將滿18歲而約他見面，給他申請建造丁屋的表格，並叫他簽名，他回家與母親商量後便簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱對簽署無印象<br />\n<br />\n被告指司理知他沒有地，說只要他「出名就有錢收」。他說司理在他滿18歲時，再致電問他「簽咗名未」並約見面，其後帶他上律師樓。他於律師樓簽署出售丁權的合同，合同上寫明他可獲20萬元報酬。他當日亦有簽署其他文件，惟稱不記得內容。<br />\n<br />\n古稱並不清楚當時將丁權賣給誰，估計是發展商決定報酬銀碼。後來他向學生資助辦事處申請學生資助，但並不知「有地係落佢名」。<br />\n<br />\n根據兩份轉讓契，辯方指當時有發展商將總值50萬的七塊地，以及價值75萬的五塊地出售予被告，被告表示他未聽聞該發展商，並不認識賣家授權人，亦未曾接觸過相關文件。辯方續問他有否簽過授權書，被告指文件上有他的簽署，惟對此事毫無印象。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4440/18<br />\n■記者廖希呈<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n牙醫涉膠水黏合病人斷齒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日提醒你：吹漲恐龍樂園"},{"pid":"2e60b9f2a05c23e352874594ab79c6e17b91c1eb","tid":1029072,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/8_sX9IR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F8_sX9IR_1200x0.png&h=66b620f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb9cbc9c698d095dda862e1282dda6d6e21287e1","tid":1029072,"uid":113929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"賣丁先賣得廿萬，隻警係咪比人食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d2030d3a3ebc9ac58dedb7bce253d86657d2f4","tid":1029072,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣丁先賣得廿萬，隻警係咪比人食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇條村係邊。有D地方的確唔撚值錢。"},{"pid":"13671a7c4fdd9172281178d17fc7d386eb2cdd0c","tid":1029072,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9cbc9c698d095dda862e1282dda6d6e21287e1","tid":1029072,"uid":113929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"賣丁先賣得廿萬，隻警係咪比人食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"廿萬好多架喇，之前又有單係10萬，應該係得西貢個d先貴"},{"pid":"ead1c51b2c44b061d28d9883d42467a6a81e5ba0","tid":1029072,"uid":74818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9cbc9c698d095dda862e1282dda6d6e21287e1","tid":1029072,"uid":113929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:33:33.000Z","msg":"賣丁先賣得廿萬，隻警係咪比人食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"有啲村得十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8466a049577a2aa71193573a7636c6df6fdcc973","tid":1029072,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor